Class OutputDecisionTreeNeo4j

java.lang.Object
main.OutputDecisionTreeNeo4j
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable
public class OutputDecisionTreeNeo4j extends Object implements AutoCloseable
This class is used to fetch nodes from graph database or from csv and call the functions to generate decision tree with confusion matrix, generation time and prediction time for the output
